      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "> Includes:\r\n> ...\r\n>    * [Fix Clang `-Wconditional-uninitialized` warning bitcoin-core/leveldb-subtree#59](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/leveldb-subtree/pull/59)\r\n\r\nThat PR [states](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/leveldb-subtree/pull/59#issue-3892325883) that it:\r\n> ... eliminates the need for the following [code](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/b58eebf1520f503bd4c7c5693546a6859064ce51/cmake/leveldb.cmake#L89-L92):\r\n> \r\n> ```cmake\r\n> else()\r\n>   try_append_cxx_flags(\"-Wconditional-uninitialized\" TARGET nowarn_leveldb_interface SKIP_LINK\r\n>     IF_CHECK_PASSED \"-Wno-conditional-uninitialized\"\r\n>   )\r\n> ```\r\n\r\nShould we remove this in an additional commit here?",
